metadata.name: Winter, On the Beach at Dawn
metadata.description:
The Magic Bus arrives at the beach at dawn,  
A symbol of life that's ever moving on.  
It's time to hop on, the sun is rising high,  
A chance to find yourself on a journey to the sky.

The destination is unknown, the path is unclear,  
But an adventure awaits with each passing year.  
The Magic Bus will take you on a new way,  
To explore your dreams and to find your own way.

The bus will take you to places far away,  
Where your spirit will soar and your heart will stay.  
So come, take a ride on the Magic Bus,  
And discover the beauty of life, without any fuss.
